Q6)Enable devtools and play around by making changes.

To enable Spring Boot DevTools, I added the following dependency in pom.xml:

<dependency>
    <groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
    <artifactId>spring-boot-devtools</artifactId>
    <optional>true</optional>
</dependency>

Then, I enabled automatic restart by setting:

spring.devtools.restart.enabled=true

I played with DevTools by:
 ->Changing a controller method and observing automatic restart.
 ->Updating application properties and seeing real-time changes without restarting.